1328
01:16:57,743 --> 01:16:59,832
Thanks, Walter.

1329
01:16:59,876 --> 01:17:02,052
[ Sighs ]

1330
01:17:02,095 --> 01:17:03,880
Hey, are you okay?

1331
01:17:03,923 --> 01:17:05,446
