1392
01:21:28,361 --> 01:21:29,885
- She fainted?
- Yeah.

1393
01:21:30,407 --> 01:21:32,800
Congratulations.
You're fantastic.

1394
01:21:32,844 --> 01:21:33,845
You won.

1395
01:21:33,889 --> 01:21:37,153
- We won?
- We won?

1396
01:21:37,196 --> 01:21:39,242
[ All cheer & holler ]

1397
