I like "Willie",
for Willie mays.

1404
01:22:10,273 --> 01:22:11,883
That's good.

1405
01:22:11,927 --> 01:22:13,189
How about "amadeus"?

1406
01:22:13,232 --> 01:22:16,192
"Amadeus"?
He won't get
beat up in school.

1407
01:22:16,235 --> 01:22:18,281
Little Wolfie...

1408
01:22:20,239 --> 01:22:21,501
To friendship,

1409
01:22:21,545 --> 01:22:23,982
and love...

