1478
01:26:08,032 --> 01:26:08,598
Coming up the steps.

1479
01:26:11,078 --> 01:26:11,731
Oh, baby.

1480
01:26:36,234 --> 01:26:38,236
Woman with a baby.
Woman with a baby.

1481
01:26:39,542 --> 01:26:42,022
Woman with a baby!
Woman with a baby.

