01:26:43,328 --> 01:26:45,243
Hey, you!
Get your hands off!

1483
01:26:45,287 --> 01:26:46,679
I'm so sorry!
So sorry!

1484
01:26:46,723 --> 01:26:48,203
Kimberly?
Honey?

1485
01:26:48,246 --> 01:26:49,508
Are you okay?

1486
01:26:55,775 --> 01:26:58,517
Hi.
We're having a baby.

1487
01:26:58,561 --> 01:27:00,693
She's having a baby.

1488
01:27:01,607 --> 01:27:03,522
