we're all in spirit.

1532
01:29:21,443 --> 01:29:23,793
Spiritual fathers?
Oh...

1533
01:29:23,836 --> 01:29:25,795
We'll need four sets
of scrubs.

1534
01:29:25,838 --> 01:29:27,623
Gentlemen,
the changing room.

1535
01:29:27,666 --> 01:29:29,320
The changing room.

1536
01:29:29,364 --> 01:29:30,843
To the changing room.

